    <h3 class="step-title">Store payroll and incentive accrual</h3>
    <p class="step-description">Commission is accrued against the month that earned it rather than the month it is paid. Two <a href="/blog/maharashtra-professional-tax-shops-act">Maharashtra profession tax</a> registrations run through the payroll, one for salaries paid and one for the business itself, and the labour welfare contribution is diarised half-yearly outside the monthly cycle.</p>
